{"tid":343473,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人男朋友呀媽煮野食好難食？","createTime":"2017-08-01T13:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T06:56:41.000Z","uid":130955,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d94b418d8fe9a2aa0389ef7c8dd35ac1528eaed1","tid":343473,"uid":130955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T13:02:55.000Z","msg":"我真心中意男朋友，<br />\n第一次上佢屋企食飯，<br />\n真係估唔到男友娘親既手勢咁掂.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n排骨有陣生生地既臭味...<br />\n菜係苦既....<br />\n最好味係白飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而因為尊重長輩，我快快咁<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咬咬咬</span>個舊排骨...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">閉氣</span>啃左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一路食一路用白飯送走佢，<br />\n喊出黎真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男女娘親問好唔好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我就答左句：都.....幾..好...味呀～ 夠哂肉味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：我男朋友到而家仲未知我吾中意佢呀媽煮既野.... 而我好擔心將來我有機會食到既每一餐「<strong>男友娘親飯</strong>」都會係咁.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實有冇同路人？？？？</span>"},{"pid":"73d0b6208370e54c2fe7e00a1a377c86e4e3ba3f","tid":343473,"uid":15814,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T13:05:01.000Z","msg":"你男朋友都鍾意食?<br />\n下次過到去自己煮 又可以加分又唔使食伯母煮既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955a8387aa583749f086b8fe02053f8e48d6a6cd","tid":343473,"uid":42539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"唔係好明點解唔同男朋友講"},{"pid":"ce6d9f42cfcc95108a412c01ba